--- !u!114 &6387373769668995793
MonoBehaviour:
  m_ObjectHideFlags: 0
  m_CorrespondingSourceObject: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabInstance: {fileID: 0}
  m_PrefabAsset: {fileID: 0}
  m_GameObject: {fileID: 7633379350428642544}
  m_Enabled: 1
  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: f4688fdb7df04437aeb418b961361dc5, type: 3}
  m_Name: 
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Unity.TextMeshPro::TMPro.TextMeshProUGUI
  m_Material: {fileID: 0}
  m_Color: {r: 1, g: 1, b: 1, a: 1}
  m_RaycastTarget: 1
  m_RaycastPadding: {x: 0, y: 0, z: 0, w: 0}
  m_Maskable: 1
  m_OnCullStateChanged:
    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: '<size=135%><color=#00E0B8><b>CONTROLS</b></color></size>

    <color=#FFA500>------------</color>

    <color=#FFFFFF>

    Use
    Arrow Keys to move the ball

    Up Arrow - Move Forward

    Left / Right Arrow
    - Rotate Direction

    </color>

    <size=135%><color=#00E0B8><b>POWER ABILITIES</b></color></size>

    <color=#FFA500>------------</color>

    <color=#FFFFFF>

    Space
    - Turbo Push

    F - Smash Attack (when Smash Power is active)

    </color>

    <size=135%><color=#00E0B8><b>POWER-UPS</b></color></size>

    <color=#FFA500>------------</color>

    <color=#FFFFFF>

    Yellow
    Power-Up - Increases hit force and push strength

    Pink Power-Up - Enables
    Smash ability that launches nearby enemies

    </color>

    <size=135%><color=#00E0B8><b>GAME
    OBJECTIVE</b></color></size>

    <color=#FFA500>------------</color>

    <color=#FFFFFF>

    Push
    enemy balls into the Enemy Goal to score

    Prevent enemies from entering your
    goal

    </color>

    <size=135%><color=#00E0B8><b>MATCH TIMER</b></color></size>

    <color=#FFA500>------------</color>

    <color=#FFFFFF>

    Score
    more goals before time runs out

    </color>

    <size=135%><color=#00E0B8><b>DIFFICULTY
    MODES</b></color></size>

    <color=#FFA500>------------</color>

    <color=#FFFFFF>

    Easy
    - Slower AI, stronger player

    Medium - Balanced gameplay

    Hard - Faster
    AI, smarter interception

    </color>'
